title: 281: Dating App Match Breakdown!
itunes:title: 281: Dating App Match Breakdown!
description:
It’s time for The Broads to go over the dating app matches from the #broadsquad - Tinder, and Hinge, and Bumble - oh my! Broad Squad members have sent in photos of matches they have had on dating apps and Bekah and Jess treat it like a Bachelor Cast Bio Breakdown and make guesses and wild assumptions about what these men may be like as dates! You may want to watch this one on Youtube, broads!

***Disclaimer: Bekah and Jess do not know these men. Faces and names have been blurred for privacy!
